        "bullet_point": {
            "value": [
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "8.25\" FIXED BLADE KNIFE: Constructed from one solid piece of 3CR13 stainless steel, this full tang hunting knife is incredibly sturdy and durable",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "DOUBLE EDGE KNIFE BLADE: Symmetrical in shape, this fixed blade knife is well balanced, lightweight and features a spear point that lines up through the center of the full tang handle",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "OVERALL COMPACT SIZE: Measuring in with a 3.5” blade and an overall length is 8.25” this knife is easy to store in small spaces like pockets, backpacks, bags, or purses",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "3CR13 STAINLESS STEEL: Made from highly durable, heavy duty steel that won’t rust, this knife is great for use indoors or outdoors; easy to clean; hand wash only. The ergonomic handle features a finger hook and weight reducing cut outs",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "STRONG KYDEX SHEATH: The ASR Tactical full tang knife comes with a sturdy black slim kydex sheath that can affix to your pocket or belt",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                }
            ],
            "is_required": true,
