        "product_description": {
            "value": [
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "The ASR Tactical spear point style knife is great for throwing. Being symmetrical in shape, it features a sharp tip that lines up with the blade’s center and will effortlessly pierce and stab. With a blade of just 3.5” in length and an overall length of 8.25”, it can easily fit inside of a pocket, backpack, or purse for quick deployment.<br/><br/>Our full tang blade features an ergonomic handle with a finger hook and comes with a sturdy black Kydex sheath so you can store the blade safely when not in use. The blade itself is constructed of heavy-duty stainless steel so you don’t need to worry about it rusting, making it great for outdoor use too.<br/><br/>This blade is a must-have tactical and self-defense tool for anyone who values their safety either indoors or outdoors. Its decorative design also makes it a great gift for knife collectors and enthusiasts.",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                }
            ],
